---
import LayoutFunnel from '@/layouts/LayoutFunnel.astro';
---

<LayoutFunnel title="Clinic Revenue Architecture | Marketing by Bešić">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-20">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-4xl text-center">
      <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-brand/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8">
        <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-brand" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1 class="heading-xl mb-6">
        Transform Your Clinic Into a Revenue Machine
      </h1>
      <p class="body-lg mb-12">
        Neurolinguistic Revenue Architecture built specifically for medical clinics. Stop leaking revenue. Start scaling predictably.
      </p>

      <!-- Hero Image Placeholder -->
      <div class="w-full h-[500px] bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#8224e3]/30 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-gray-500 mb-12">[HERO IMAGE PLACEHOLDER: 1200x600]</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="heading-lg mb-8 text-center">The Hidden Revenue Leak in Your Clinic</h2>
      <p class="body-md mb-6">
        Most clinics lose 30-40% of potential revenue due to outdated tracking, poor patient follow-up, and infrastructure that doesn't convert. You're spending on ads, but the leaks are eating your margins alive.
      </p>
      <p class="body-md">
        Our Diagnostic Protocol identifies every leak in your system and builds a compensation model that only charges you on verified net-new revenue.
      </p>

      <!-- Image Placeholder -->
      <div class="w-full h-[300px] bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#8224e3]/30 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-gray-500 my-12">[IMAGE PLACEHOLDER: 800x400]</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="heading-lg mb-8 text-center">The NRA Clinic Framework</h2>

      <!-- Phase 1 -->
      <div class="bg-bg-secondary border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 mb-6 text-left">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-brand font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-2">Phase 1: 30-Day Diagnostic Audit</h3>
            <p class="body-md">
              Zero ad spend. We set up EMR API tracking, analyze your current patient journey, and identify every revenue leak. You'll receive a comprehensive diagnostic report with actionable insights.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 2 -->
      <div class="bg-bg-secondary border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 mb-6 text-left">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-brand font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-2">Phase 2: Infrastructure Activation</h3>
            <p class="body-md">
              We deploy NLP-optimized patient communication, build conversion infrastructure, and integrate with your existing EMR system. Every touchpoint is engineered to convert.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 3 -->
      <div class="bg-bg-secondary border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 text-left">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-brand font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-2">Phase 3: Compensation Model</h3>
            <p class="body-md">
              You only pay on verified net-new revenue. No vanity metrics. No wasted ad spend. Pure, measurable growth tied directly to your bottom line.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Image Placeholder -->
      <div class="w-full h-[300px] bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#8224e3]/30 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-gray-500 my-12">[IMAGE PLACEHOLDER: 800x400]</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Execution Gap Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-[#111111] relative z-10">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="heading-lg mb-8 text-center">The Execution Gap</h2>
      <p class="body-md mb-6 text-center">
        Most agencies deliver reports. We deliver revenue. The gap between knowing your leaks and fixing them is where businesses die. Our framework closes that gap by implementing, tracking, and optimizing every touchpoint in your patient journey.
      </p>
      <p class="body-md text-center">
        While your competitors are still waiting for proposals, your clinic will already be capturing the revenue they're leaving on the table.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA / Calendar Section -->
  <section class="py-20 pb-48">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl text-center">
      <h2 class="heading-lg mb-6">Schedule Your Diagnostic Audit</h2>
      <p class="body-lg mb-12">
        Book a free 15-minute call to see if your clinic qualifies for the NRA framework.
      </p>

      <!-- Booking Button -->
      <div class="mt-12 flex justify-center w-full">
        <a
          href="https://calendar.app.google/EnAH7N1F2bYFdUa9A"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-white transition-all duration-300 bg-[#8224e3] rounded-lg hover:bg-[#6a1ca6] hover:scale-105 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(130,36,227,0.4)]"
        >
          Book Your Diagnostic Call
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</LayoutFunnel>
